      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRIXIE MAHACK (8) latest effort finished 4th in a Grade 4/5 on February 23 over 630m at this track behind Lumeah Nancy beaten 7 lengths (37.11). With a clean break looks hard to beat. ASHES TO ASHES (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 8 last run (20.88) at this track. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including three wins, from six starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. SUNSHINE SANDY (7) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (30.05) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to be in the finish again. ANGRY GOLIATH (3) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
